zreap
-----

Reap zombie processes.

BUILD
  The binary "zreap" can be built by running:

    $ make

  The source also includes a simple test that can be run with:

    $ make test

  Clean-up build artifacts with:

    $ make clean

USAGE
  zreap -p PPID -z PID [-z PID]...

ARGUMENTS
  -p  PID of the parent process.
  -z  A list of one (or more) zombie sub-process PIDs.
